name: Stardust, Infinite
description:
The journey in NFT community space, begin with a magical or charismatic quality or feeling.
Looped in a limitless or endless in space, extent, or size; that is impossible to measure or calculate.
May the strong forces continue to strive. To the moon! and beyond!
Text by : Iqbal Febrian P (qblfp)

______________________________________

This work symbolizes the meaning of infinite, eternal, repeating pattern. infinity is a representation of the NFT community, which grow and support each other, fire symbolizes passion, and bubbles symbolize difference.
this work is my gratitude towards the NFT community, please take this work and share your "infinite" side to others people. Big Lovee.
To Infinity! and beyond!
Text by: Wendi AF (BubbleSpeedz)
